0also%20happened%20during%20the%202019%20election.%20We%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20(no%20hearing%20has%20been%20held%20so%20far)%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20not%20reacted%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20has%2C%20however%2C%20offered%20disgruntled%20candidates%20options%20to%20re-check%20vote-counts%2C%20including%20picking%20machines%20from%20any%20polling%20station%20in%20a%20seat%20and%20opting%20for%20a%20mock%20poll%20and%20VVPAT%20slip%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-gives-aggrieved-candidates-choice-on-how-they-want-to-check-evms-6117292%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPoll%20Body%20Gives%20Candidates%20Choice%20On%20How%20To%20Check%20EVMs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20such%20applications%20have%20been%20received%2C%20the%20EC%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20published%20by%20ADR%20on%20its%20website%2C%20in%20the%20former%20case%20(i.e.%2C%20in%20which%20more%20votes%20were%20counted%20than%20polled)%20the%20discrepancy%20was%20between%20one%20and%203%2C811%20votes%20in%20each%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20each%20case%20the%20winning%20margin%20was%20significantly%20larger%20than%20that%20discrepancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDiscrepancies%20between%20the%20votes%20cast%20and%20the%20votes%20counted%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3A%20Multiple%20Perspectives%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FADRReport%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ADRReport%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrSEYBMz5iq%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrSEYBMz5iq%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20donate%20to%20ADR%2C%20click%20here%3