0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-bjp-won-in-surat-even-before-vote-counting-began-5812797%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20BJP%20Won%20In%20Surat%20Even%20Before%20Vote%20Counting%20Began%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20this%20data%20comes%20a%20day%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20resumes%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20ADR%20seeking%20release%20of%20all%20voter%20turnout%20numbers%2C%20including%20votes%20rejected%20for%20various%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20our%20petition%20on%20this%20matter...%20we%20will%20present%20before%20the%20court%20the%20latest%20facts%20related%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20which%20have%20come%20out%20through%20affidavits.%20We%20will%20tell%20the%20court%20what%20happened%20in%202019%20has%20happened%20again%20in%202024...%20and%20will%20say%20action%20needs%20to%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-form-17c-voter-turnout-data-case-in-an-election-hands-off-supreme-court-adjourns-voter-turnout-data-plea-5734479%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIn%20An%20Election%2C%20Hands%20Off!%26quot%3B%20Top%20Court%20Adjourns%20Voter%20Turnout%20Data%20Plea%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiled%20mid-election%2C%20the%20ADR%20had%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20compile%20and%20publish%20this%20data%20on%20its%20website%20after%20each%20phase.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20the%20plea%2C%20noting%20that%20doing%20so%20could%20%26quot%3Boverburden%26quot%3B%20the%20poll%20panel%20during%20the%20election%20and%20that%20five%20of%20seven%20phases%20were%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20May.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20would%20re-list%20the%20matter%20after%20the%20election%20and%20its%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Form%2017C%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heart%20of%20that%20matter%20was%20the%20ADR%20seeking%20scanned%20copies%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fform-17c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForm%2017C%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20a%20record%20of%20votes%20cast%20at%20each%20polling%20station%20across%20the%20country%20-%20to%20be%20published%20after%20each%20phase.%20This%20document%20is%20key%20because%20voter%20turnout%20data%20in%20this%20form%20can%20be%20used%20to%20legally%20challenge%20an%20election%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20was%20sought%20by%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20activists%20after%20the%20EC%20delayed%20release%20of%20first%20and%20second%20phase%20voter%20turnout%20figures.%20When%20published%2C%20there%20were%20questions%20over%20differences%20in%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explains-form-17c-and-row-over-poll-panels-voter-turnout-data-5728033%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForm%2017C%20And%20Row%20Over%20Poll%20Panel's%20Voter%20Turnout%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVVPAT%20Row%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20the%20ADR%20got%20a%20stern%20warning%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20petition%20asking%20that%20all%20EVM%20votes%20be%20verified%20through%20paper%20slips%20generated%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20(Voter-Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail)%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-evm-vvpat-supreme-court-raises-doubts-about-petitioners-bonafides-in-evm-case-5529884%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEffort%20To%20Discredit%20India's%20Progress%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Raps%20VVPAT%20P