a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-return-refunds-stores-likely-temporary-fix-to-growing-problem-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno-return%20refunds%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20happen%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20and%20Amazon%20says%20a%20group%20calling%20itself%20Chin%20Chopa%20has%20become%20a%20specialist%20at%20exploiting%20several%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%2C%20as%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20Amazon%20customers%20would%20share%20their%20login%20credentials%20with%20a%20person%20from%20Chin%20Chopa%20who%20would%20initiate%20a%20refund%20process%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chin%20Chopa%20operators%20would%20then%20fabricate%20a%20story%20for%20Amazon%20customer%20service%20representatives%20%E2%80%94%20in%20some%20cases%20using%20falsified%20police%20reports%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20the%20company%20to%20return%20money%20to%20the%20customer's%20account%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20would%20then%20pay%20Chin%20Chopa%20a%20fee%20in%20cryptocurrency%20of%20roughly%2020%25%20to%2030%25%20of%20the%20product's%20actual%20price%2C%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20beginning%20of%202023%2C%20Chin%20Chopa%20has%20posted%20over%20%241%2C260%2C464.18%20in%20vouches%20for%20Amazon%20refunds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%20Vouches%20refer%20to%20the%20screenshots%20posted%20as%20proof%20of%20funds%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lawsuit%20does%20not%20identify%20the%20operators%20of%20the%20Telegram%20account%2C%20it%20does%20name%20seven%20US%20defendants%20and%20one%20Canadian%20who%20are%20said%20to%20have%20used%20and%20promoted%20the%20illegal%20service%20to%20obtain%20products%2C%20including%20multiple%20MacBook%20Pro%20laptops%20and%20an%20iPad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20the%20defendants%20have%20not%20been%20identified%20on%20the%20federal%20court%20docket.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20customers%20are%20responsible%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20activities%20that%20occur%20under%20their%20account%20or%20password%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20Conditions%20of%20Use%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20Chopa%20is%20the%20second%20major%20group%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20to%20be%20targeted%20by%20Amazon's%20Customer%20Protection%20%26amp%3B%20Enforcement%20team.%20An%20earlier%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%20against%20a%20group%20based%20in%20Lithuania%20known%20as%20Rekk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Wendell%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20CPE%20team%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7221552137388929024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20these%20groups%20and%20others%20like%20it%20are%20collectively%20responsible%20for%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20losses%20across%20three%20continents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20is%20addressing%20this%20issue%20head-on%20through%20the%20development%20of%20tools%20that%20use%20machine%20learning%20models%20to%20proactively%20detect%20and%20prevent%20fraud%2C%20as%20well%20as%20employing%20specialized%20teams%20dedicated%20to%20detecting%2C%20investigating%20and%20stopping%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20lawsuit%20sends%20a%20strong%20message%20that%20participating%20in%20fraudulent%20refund%20schemes%20has%20severe%20consequences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-suing-refund-fraud-group-it-says-stole-10000-items-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722337382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a80bd0fb6d32635ee4c3f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-suing-refund-fraud-group-it-says-stole-10000-items-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon's%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20group%20named%20%26quot%3BChin%20Chopa%26quot%3B%20also%20names%20seven%20US%20defendants%20who%20the%20company%20says%20used%20and%20promoted%20the%20illegal%20service.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-suing-refund-fraud-group-it-says-stole-10000-items-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20say%20weight-loss%20drugs%20could%20protect%20our%20brains%20from%20dementia.%20Early%20results%20suggest%20they're%20onto%20something.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22liraglutide%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a80ccf1a227600e6329f9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiraglutide%2C%20like%20semaglutide%2C%20is%20manufactured%20by%20Novo%20Nordisk.%3Cp%3EUCG%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAbout%20100%20Alzheimer's%20patients%20tested%20out%20a%20daily%20weight%20loss%20injection%20to%20help%20their%20disease.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20saw%20meaningful%20differences%20in%20memory%20test%20scores%20and%20brain%20loss%2C%20when%20compared%20to%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20say%20whether%20GLP-1s%20can%20be%20used%20for%20dementia%2C%20but%20this%20looks%20promising.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDiabetes%2C%20weight%20loss%2C%20heart%20disease%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-zepbound-sleep-apnea-conditions-glp1-drugs-treat-l2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esleep%20apnea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20now%20%E2%80%A6%20dementia%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20are%20racing%20to%20discover%20whether%20the%20new%20class%20of%20weight-loss%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20originally%20approved%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20might%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-treat-addiction-alzheimers-depression-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erepurposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20treat%20all%20kinds%20of%20other%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20dementia%20researchers%20from%20the%20UK%20released%20some%20early%20results%20that%20suggest%20it's%20possible%20these%20trendy%20injections%20might%20also%20stall%20the%20progression%20of%20dementia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20were%20announced%20at%20the%20Alzheimer's%20Association%20International%20Conference%20in%20Philadelphia%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20have%20not%20been%20published%20in%20a%20peer-reviewed%20science%20journal%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20independent%20experts%20say%20we%20shouldn't%20get%20too%20excited%20just%20yet.%20Still%2C%20the%20study%20authors%20insist%20this%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20promising%20area%20of%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e999ffd5-a2ba-4f34-832f-b867e12e3fd1%5C%22%3EA%20daily%20injection%20for%20brain%20preservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GLP%201%20injection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a80c401a227600e6329f8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIuliia%20Burmistrova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20study%2C%20researchers%20spent%20a%20year%20tracking%20brain%20changes%20across%20204%20Alzheimer's%20patients%20with%20mild%20to%20moderate%20disease.%20Half%20of%20the%20group%20received%20a%20placebo%20drug.%20The%20other%20half%20received%20a%20daily%20dose%20of%20liraglutide%2C%20a%20medication%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20same%20class%20of%20drugs%20as%20Ozempic%2C%20Mounjaro%2C%20and%20Wegovy.%20(They%20all%20mimic%20a%20hormone%20called%20GLP-1%2C%20which%20makes%20you%20feel%20full.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20study%20wasn't%20able%20to%20successfully%20achieve%20every%20outcome%20it%20aimed%20for%2C%20it%20did%20appear%20to%20show%20the%20shots%20having%20some%20positive%20effect%20on%20both%20cognitive%20function%20and%20brain%20volume%20preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20an%20open%20question%20whether%20injectables%20for%20weight%20loss%20can%20help%20slow%20down%20this%20brain%20disease.%20Because%20so%20many%20different%20factors%20appear%20to%20influence%20how%20Alzheimer's%20progresses%20over%20time%2C%20experts%20are%20starting%20to%20coalesce%20around%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20will%20likely%20never%20be%20one%20single%20drug%20that%20can%20treat%20Alzheimer's%20outright.%20Patients%20may%20need%20an%20ever-evolving%20cocktail%20of%20different%20things%20to%20preserve%20whatever%20brain%20function%20they%20have%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20hard%20to%20make%20sensible%20critiques%20on%20only%20an%20abstract%20and%20press%20release%2C%20without%20the%20full%20details%20of%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephen%20Evans%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Hygiene%20and%20Tropical%20Medicine%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20this%20study%2C%20told%20the%20Science%20Media%20Centre.%20%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20like%20it%20is%20worth%20pursuing%20a%20larger%20trial%2C%20but%20these%20results%20cannot%20demonstrate%20that%20liraglutide%20can%20protect%20against%20dementia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268875a75-3466-4a49-8de8-d96777812fde%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'statin'%20for%20the%20brain%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%239%20%20%20JasonKirk_2Neurons%20nsw2020%20winner%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f84dcce91aa9e001880b277%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConnections%20between%20hippocampal%20neurons%20(brain%20cells).%3Cp%3EJason%20Kirk%20%26amp%3B%20Quynh%20Nguyen%2FNikon%20Small%20World%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20who%20started%20this%20trial%20ended%20up%20enjoying%20taking%20liraglutide%20every%20day.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trial%2C%2023%20of%20the%20102%20participants%20assigned%20to%20treatment%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20study%20(compared%20to%20only%2015%20dropouts%20on%20placebo.)%20Many%20taking%20the%20drug%20complained%20of%20nausea%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommon%20side%20effects%20of%20GLP-1%3C%2Fa%3E%20drugs%2C%20which%20work%20to%20regulate%20blood%20sugar%2C%20and%20end%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-ozempic-glp1-drugs-developed-by-gila-monster-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslowing%20down%20digestion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20those%20who%20stuck%20with%20the%20shots%20seemed%20to%20display%20better%20final%20performance%20on%20their%20memory%20tests%20than%20their%20peers%20who%20hadn't%20injected%20GLP-1s.%20Doctors%20also%20saw%20about%2050%25%20less%20volume%20loss%20in%20key%20areas%20of%20their%20brains%20on%20MRI%20scans%2C%20including%20parts%20of%20the%20brain%20responsible%20for%20memory%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20slower%20loss%20of%20brain%20volume%20suggests%20liraglutide%20protects%20the%20brain%2C%20much%20like%20statins%20protect%20the%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Paul%20Edison%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20neuroscience%20at%20Imperial%20College%20London%20who%20led%20the%20study%2C%20said%20in%20a%20release.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20further%20research%20is%20needed%2C%20liraglutide%20may%20work%20through%20various%20mechanisms%2C%20such%20as%20reducing%20inflammation%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20lowering%20insulin%20resistance%20and%20the%20toxic%20effects%20of%20Alzheimer's%20biomarkers%20amyloid-beta%20and%20tau%2C%20and%20improving%20how%20the%20brain's%20nerve%20cells%20communicate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20liraglutide%20didn't%20appear%20to%20do%20for%20the%20patients%20in%20this%20trial%20was%20meaningfully%20improve%20their%20brain's%20glucose%20metabolism%2C%20which%20is%20another%20key%20part%20of%20dementia%20progression.%20This%20was%20the%20main%20goal%20of%20the%20trial.%20Experts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D40355e7b849b7867bf32f60d07c1ddac320bcaa39cbf2113d9adf776020950e4%26postID%3D66a809a76550c8ac4ef487c2%26postSlug%3Dglp-1-for-dementia-alzheimers-early-study-looks-promising-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41583-019-0132-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20seen%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20dementia%20patients'%20brains%20get%20worse%20and%20worse%20at%20efficiently%20using%20glucose%20for%20energy%20as%20their%20disease%20progresses%2C%20but%20the%20calculus%20is%20always%20complicated.%20With%20Alzheimer's%2C%20it's%20been%20especially%20difficult%20for%20scientists%20to%20untangle%20cause%20from%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdison%2C%20a%20leading%20expert%20in%20brain%20imaging%20for%20Alzheimer's%20and%20other%20neurodegenerative%20diseases%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20still%20believes%20there%20may%20be%20an%20effect.%20He%20thinks%20this%20study%20was%20too%20small%20to%20show%20a%20meaningful%20difference%20in%20glucose%20metabolism%2C%20and%20that%20GLP-1%20drugs%20may%20also%20influence%20the%20brain%20in%20more%20complex%20ways%20than%20we%20understand.%20Edison%20said%20future%20studies%20should%20focus%20less%20on%20markers%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20and%20more%20on%20%26quot%3Bcognitive%26quot%3B%20results%2C%20like%20patient%20performance%20on%20memory%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20drugs%20recently%20approved%20to%20treat%20Alzheimer's%20also%20aim%20to%20slow%20down%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20patients%20lose%20their%20memories%20and%20reasoning%20skills%2C%20but%20they%20work%20differently%20from%20GLP-1s.%20Lecanemab%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20last%20year%2C%20and%20donanemab%2C%20out%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20are%20both%20antibody%20treatments%20built%20around%20the%20idea%20that%20reducing%20the%20presence%20of%20key%20amyloid%20plaques%20in%20the%20brain%20will%20help%20slow%20dementia%20progression.%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20at%20least%20partially%20true%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20whole%20story.%20Maybe%20GLP-1%20drugs%20can%20serve%20a%20slightly%20different%20purpose%20in%20dementia%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBigger%20studies%20using%20more%20powerful%20GLP-1%20drugs%20for%20dementia%20are%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falz-journals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1002%2Falz.062415%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Novo%20Nordisk%20is%20testing%20out%20semaglutide%20(that's%20the%20drug%20branded%20as%20Ozempic%20for%20diabetes%2C%20and%20Wegovy%20for%20weight%20loss)%20as%20a%20possible%20Alzheimer's%20drug%20in%20a%20major%20worldwide%20trial%20expected%20to%20recruit%20more%20than%201%2C800%20people%20across%2038%20countries.%20Results%20are%20expected%20in%202025%2C%20and%20will%20hinge%20on%20memory%20test%20scores%2C%20not%20glucose%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglp-1-for-dementia-alzheimers-early-study-looks-promising-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722337262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a80a26fb6d32635ee4c39b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglp-1-for-dementia-alzheimers-early-study-looks-promising-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patients%20with%20Alzheimer's%20who%20took%20a%20GLP-1%20drug%20improved%20their%20memory%20scores%20and%20lost%20less%20of%20their%20brains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglp-1-for-dementia-alzheimers-early-study-looks-promising-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22McDonald's%20has%20started%20selling%20an%20even%20bigger%20burger%20%E2%80%94%20the%2014-ounce%20Big%20Arch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20McDonald's%20logo%20is%20displayed%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20on%20July%2022%2C%202024%20in%20Burbank%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a8c344fb6d32635ee4cf4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMcDonald's%20CEO%20said%20the%20company%20has%20launched%20trials%20of%20a%20bigger%2C%20%26quot%3Bmore%20satiating%26quot%3B%20burger%20in%20Canada%20and%20Portugal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Big%20Arch%20contains%20two%20beef%20patties%2C%20three%20slices%20of%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20new%20Big%20Arch%20sauce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20burger%20weighs%20in%20at%2014%20ounces%20and%20contains%201%2C065%20calories%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-expensive-prices-too-high-fast-food-restaurant-falling-sales-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20launched%20trials%20of%20a%20bigger%2C%20%26quot%3Bmore%20satiating%26quot%3B%20burger%20in%20Canada%20and%20Portugal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20revealed%20the%20name%20of%20the%20product%2C%20which%20executives%20have%20been%20teasing%20since%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Big%20Arch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20innovate%20across%20our%20core%20menu%20to%20address%20unmet%20customer%20needs%20with%20a%20more%20satiating%20burger%20that%20will%20provide%20great%20value%20for%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Chris%20Kempczinski%20told%20investors%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20contains%20two%20beef%20patties%2C%20three%20slices%20of%20white%20processed%20cheese%2C%20crispy%20onions%2C%20raw%20onions%2C%20pickles%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20a%20new%20Big%20Arch%20sauce%20in%20a%20sesame%20seed%20bun%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcdonalds.pt%2Fprodutos%2Fmcmenu%2Fsanduiches%2Fbig-arch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescription%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20burger%20on%20the%20McDonald's%20Portugal%20website.%20Kempczinski%20described%20the%20orange%20sauce%20as%20%26quot%3Btangy%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20call%20with%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20quintessential%20McDonald's%20burger%20with%20a%20twist%20on%20our%20iconic%20familiar%20flavors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20first%20announced%20plans%20for%20the%20burger%20last%20December%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-to-start-selling-bigger-burgers-menu-fast-food-restaurants-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20burger%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20is%20being%20piloted%20in%20three%20international%20markets%20this%20year%2C%20Kempczinski%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20plan%20to%20attest%20and%20learn%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20to%20gather%20learnings%20before%20scaling%20more%20broadly%20internationally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20started%20selling%20the%20Big%20Arch%20at%20selected%20restaurants%20in%20Ontario%20and%20Alb