he%20rain%20which%20fell%20over%20Paris%20on%20July%2026%20and%2027%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20poor%20quality%20of%20the%20water%20in%20the%20historically%20polluted%20Seine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftriathlon.org%2Fuploads%2Fdocs%2FWorld_Triathlon_Water_Quality_Statement%2BMatrix1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIts%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20a%20maximum%20number%20of%20E.%20Coli%20or%20Enterococci%20colonies%20per%20100%20milliliters%20at%20900%2C%20and%20a%20maximum%20number%20of%20Enterococci%20colonies%20at%20330.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20say%20what%20the%20readings%20were%2C%20only%20that%20they%20were%20too%20high%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20river's%20pollution%20levels%20have%20long%20been%20a%20topic%20of%20concern%20%E2%80%94%20swimming%20in%20the%20river%20was%20banned%20for%20100%20years%20before%20the%20Paris%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20mounted%20a%20huge%20effort%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20river%20for%20the%20contest%2C%20with%20the%20Paris%20city%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paris.fr%2Fen%2Fpages%2Fbathing-in-the-seine-will-be-possible-in-2025-27102%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epegging%20the%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20%241.5%20billion%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20officials%2C%20including%20Paris%20Mayor%20Anne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fsport%2Farticle%2F2024%2F07%2F17%2Fanne-hidalgo-s-est-baignee-dans-la-seine_6251469_3242%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHidalgo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20French%20sports%20minister%2C%20swam%20in%20the%20river%20in%20recent%20weeks%20to%20prove%20it%20was%20sage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Emmanuel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fsport%2Farticle%2F2024%2F02%2F29%2Fparis-2024-emmanuel-macron-assure-qu-il-se-baignera-dans-la-seine_6219336_3242.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacron%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20would%20but%20did%20not%20end%20up%20m