r%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fbhumi-pednekar-ups-the-style-quotient-in-a-chic-crop-top-and-stylish-skirt%2Fphotostory%2F112136319.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Are%20So%20Many%20Tech%20Graduates%20In%20India%20Unemployable%3F%20It's%20The%20'Cliff%20Effect'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fkqpg1ij_unemployment_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20tech%20graduate%2C%20full%20of%20potential%2C%20steps%20into%20the%20job%20market%2C%20only%20to%20find%20their%20skills%20outdated%20and%20their%20opportunities%20limited.%20This%20scenario%20is%20all%20too%20common%20in%20India%2C%20where%20despite%20substantial%20investments%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20a%20stark%20divide%20has%20emerged%20among%20students%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20computer%20science%20stream.%20I%20call%20this%20phenomenon%20the%20'Cliff%20Effect'%20as%20it%20highlights%20the%20precipitous%20drop%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20beyond%20top-tier%20tech%20institutes%20like%20the%20IITs%20and%20IIScs.%20This%20'cliff'%2C%20which%20leaves%20many%20students%20underprepared%20and%20alienated%20from%20cutting-edge%20advancements%2C%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20reform%20in%20India's%20computer%20science%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ESquandering%20The%20Demographic%20Dividend%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%2065%25%20of%20India's%20population%20is%20under%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20Yet%2C%20many%20lack%20the%20necessary%20skills%20required%20to%20function%20in%20a%20modern%20economy.%20According%20to%20the%20recent%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20just%20about%20half%20of%20India's%20youth%20is%20employable.%20Another%20report%2C%20by%20NASSCOM%2C%20flags%20a%20significant%20employability%20gap%20among%20engineering%20graduates%20in%20India.%20This%20gap%20has%20far-reaching%20implications%2C%20considering%20that%20India%20aims%20to%20become%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy%20by%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20computer%20science%20education%20across%20many%20Indian%20institutions%20is%20far%20from%20what's%20needed%20in%20today's%20job%20market.%20Universities%20do%20not%20update%20their%20syllabi%20frequently%2C%20leaving%20students%20unprepared%20for%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20industry.%20The%20lack%20of%20experiential%20learning%20and%20hands-on%20training%20further%20exacerbates%20the%20problem.%20Compounding%20all%20these%20issues%20is%20the%20stagnant%20entry-level%20pay%20offered%20by%20some%20major%20IT%20companies%20in%20India.%20Despite%20the%20industry's%20growth%2C%20salaries%20have%20seen%20little%20change%20over%20the%20years.%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20major%20company's%20campus%20placement%20offer%20was%20just%20about%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20annum%2C%20compared%20to%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%204.15%20lakh%20per%20annum%20a%20decade%20ago.%20The%20stagnation%20indicates%20the%20lack%20of%20value%20ascribed%20to%20fresh%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20all%20in%20all%2C%20needs%20a%20systemic%20overhaul%20in%20education%20and%20industry%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeyond%20Just%20'Coding'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20how%20to%20code%20is%20no%20longer%20enough.%20Thanks%20to%20AI%2C%20the%20job%20landscape%20is%20evolving%20rapidly%2C%20and%20employers%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20will%20seek%20candidates%20with%20deep%20domain%20knowledge%20and%20an%20interdisciplinary%20approach%20to%20problem-solving.%20This%20shift%20will%20be%20crucial%20because%20technology%20alone%20cannot%20drive%20innovation%3B%20it%20must%20be%20complemented%20by%20a%20thorough%20understanding%20of%20the%20domain%20in%20which%20it%20is%20applied.%20Only%20then%20can%20solutions%20be%20developed%20to%20effectively%20address%20real-world%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20coder%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20agriculture%20can%20design%20AI-driven%20solutions%20to%20optimise%20crop%20yields%2C%20manage%20pest%20control%2C%20and%20predict%20weather%20patterns%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20productivity%20and%20sustainability%20in%20the%20agricultural%20sector.%20Similarly%2C%20a%20coder%20who%20understands%20pedagogy%20can%20develop%20advanced%20learning%20platforms%20that%20cater%20to%20diverse%20educational%20needs%2C%20personalise%20learning%20experiences%2C%20and%20track%20student%20progress%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20stands%20to%20benefit%20significantly%20from%20computer%20scientists%20who%20possess%20interdisciplinary%20skills%20and%20don't%20rely%20solely%20on%20technical%20knowledge.%20In%20that%20light%2C%20integrating%20interdisciplinary%20courses%20in%20computer%20science%20education%20is%20important%20to%20foster%20a%20holistic%20understanding%20of%20technology%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20society.%20It%20is%20essential%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20technologists%20embodies%20responsible%20and%20trustworthy%20AI%20values%20and%20is%20aware%20of%20and%20actively%20addressing%20challenges%20like%20privacy%2C%20security%2C%20and%20other%20ethical%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Interdisciplinary%20Framework%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20an%20interdisciplinary%20approach%20to%20India's%20computer%20science%20education%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20foster%20collaborations%20between%20universities%2C%20industry%20experts%2C%20and%20policymakers%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20curriculum%20is%20both%20relevant%20and%20future-proof.%20Universities%20should%20design%20programmes%20that%20include%20mandatory%20courses%20on%20ethics%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20cybersecurity%2C%20and%20AI.%20Incorporating%20case%20studies%20and%20practical%20examples%20from%20various%20industries%20can%20help%20students%20grasp%20the%20real-world%20applications%20of%20their%20technical%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPractical%20training%20should%20be%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20this%20interdisciplinary%20approach.%20Internships%2C%20live%20projects%2C%20and%20workshops%20should%20be%20mandatory%20components.%20Establishing%20partnerships%20with%20other%20academic%20departments%20can%20promote%20cross-disciplinary%20projects%2C%20fostering%20a%20holistic%20understanding%20of%20technology's%20impact%20on%20different%20fields.%20Additionally%2C%20universities%20should%20create%20platforms%20for%20students%20to%20engage%20with%20industry%20professionals%20through%20guest%20lectures%2C%20mentorship%20programmes%2C%20and%20industry-led%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMozilla%20Foundation's%20Responsible%20Computing%20Challenge%20in%20India%20(RCC)%2C%20backed%20by%20USAID%2C%20exemplifies%20this%20approach.%20It%20funds%20and%20supports%20the%20development%20of%20curricula%20that%20combine%20computer%20science%20with%20ethics%2C%20social%20sciences%2C%20and%20interdisciplinary%20knowledge.%20The%20RCC%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20teaching%20of%20technology%20and%20computer%20science%20by%20embedding%20responsible%20computing%20practices%20into%20the%20education%20system.%20By%20integrating%20ethics%20and%20interdisciplinary%20approaches%20into%20computer%20science%20curricula%2C%20RCC%20fosters%20a%20more%20inclusive%20computational%20future%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20culture%20of%20ethical%20innovation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreaking%20The%20Status%20Quo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20an%20interdisciplinary%20approach%20in%20computer%20science%20education%20is%20fraught%20with%20challenges.%20One%20significant%20obstacle%20is%20the%20institutional%20framework%2C%20which%20often%20clings%20to%20the%20status%20quo.%20Many%20institutions%20are%20resistant%20to%20reform.%20While%20most%20educators%20are%20dedicated%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20for%20their%20students%2C%20a%20substantial%20number%20also%20harbour%20a%20%26quot%3Bthis-is-how-we-have-always-done-it%26quot%3B%20attitude%2C%20which%20hinders%20progress%20and%20innovation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20is%20a%20crucial%20need%20to%20convince%20parents%20to%20think%20beyond%20traditional%20programmes.%20Many%20parents%2C%20understandably%2C%20want%20their%20kids%20to%20follow%20'safe%20bet'%2C%20conventional%20career%20paths%20over%20more%20innovative%20and%20interdisciplinary%20fields.%20Changing%20this%20mindset%20is%20vital%20for%20students%20to%20have%20diverse%20educational%20experiences%20that%20equip%20them%20with%20the%20skills%20needed%20for%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20modern%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jibu%20Elias%20is%20an%20AI%20ethicist%2C%20activist%2C%20researcher%2C%20and%20currently%20the%20Country%20Lead%20(India)%20for%20the%20Responsible%20Computing%20Challenge%20at%20Mozilla%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722335220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8glk6m7g_unemployment_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-are-so-many-indian-tech-graduates-unemployable-blame-the-cliff-effect-6222152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Knowing%20how%20to%20code%20is%20no%20longer%20enough.%20Thanks%20to%20AI%2C%20the%20job%20landscape%20is%20evolving%20rapidly%2C%20and%20employers%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20will%20seek%20candidates%20with%20deep%20domain%20knowledge%20and%20an%20interdisciplinary%20approach%20to%20problem-solving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni