-2023-24-which-is-the-correct-income-tax-return-form-for-salaried-taxpayers-itr-1-or-itr-2-find-out%2Farticleshow%2F112134476.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akhilesh%20Yadav%20vs%20Anurag%20Thakur%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20Over%20Agnipath%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20Budget%202024%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20saw%20an%20explosive%20exchange%20between%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Anurag%20Thakur%20over%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%2C%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Kannauj%2C%20said%20this%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbudget%20of%20despair%26quot%3B%20but%20people%20in%20the%20government%20are%20praising%20it.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20the%20unemployed%2C%20youngsters%20and%20villages.%20%26quot%3BThose%20with%20family%20know%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20run%20the%20household%2C%20provide%20education%20to%20children%20and%20take%20care%20of%20the%20treatment%20of%20the%20elderly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShifting%20focus%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20showed%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20dream%2C%20but%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20did%20not%20get%20any%20big%20project%20even%20though%20we%20got%20a%20Prime%20Minister.%20Did%20we%20get%20an%20IIM%20or%20an%20IIT%3F%20Which%20central%20institution%20was%20set%20up%3F%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20gave%20land%20for%20two%20AIIMS%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20Gorakhpur%2C%20but%20are%20people%20getting%20adequate%20treatment%20there%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20lack-lustre%20show%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20this%20general%20election%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BResults%20in%20UP%20showed%20how%20much%20you%20worked%2C%20would%20results%20be%20like%20this%20if%20you%20did%20everything%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20quoted%20shayari%20by%20Wasim%20Barelvi.%20%26quot%3BWoh%20jhoot%20bol%20raha%20tha%20bade%20salike%20se%2C%20main%20aitbaar%20na%20karta%20toh%20kya%20karta%3F%20(He%20lied%20with%20such%20finesse%2C%20I%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20believe)%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20to%20cheers%20from%20the%20Opposition%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20train%20derailment%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20over%2C%20there%20is%20a%20competition%20between%20rail%20accidents%20and%20paper%20leaks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20questioned%20if%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20fulfilled%20its%20promise%20of%20doubling%20farmers'%20income.%20%26quot%3BYou%20say%20you%20are%20giving%20MSP%20(Minimum%20Support%20Price)%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20denying%20a%20legal%20guarantee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20for%20short-term%20recruitment%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20youngster%20preparing%20to%20join%20the%20forces%20can%20accept%20it.%20When%20this%20scheme%20came%2C%20prominent%20industrialists%20were%20asked%20to%20tweet%20that%20there%20is%20no%20better%20job%20and%20they%20will%20rehire%20them%20(Agniveers)%20once%20their%20four-year%20stint%20ended.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20government%20knows%20it%20is%20not%20a%20good%20scheme%2C%20that's%20why%20it%20is%20asking%20BJP-led%20state%20governments%20to%20give%20job%20quota%20to%20Agniveers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20opposed%20his%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20dared%20him%20to%20say%20that%20Agnipath%20is%20a%20good%20scheme%20and%20sat%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20come%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20country%20its%20first%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra%20awardee%2C%20the%20late%20Major%20Somnath%20Sharma.%20Most%20martyrs%20in%20Kargil%20were%20from%20Himachal.%20It%20is%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20that%20fulfilled%20the%20long-pending%20demand%20of%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%2C%20Agniveer%20has%20100%20per%20cent%20employment%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20then%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20what%20is%20the%20need%20for%20state%20governments%20giving%20quota%20(for%20Agniveers).%20I%20went%20to%20a%20military%20school%2C%20we%20can%20also%20count%20Param%20Vir%20Chakras.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Union%20Minister%20stood%20up%20again%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20just%20gone%20to%20a%20military%20school%2C%20I%20am%20serving%20as%20Territorial%20Army%20captain.%20Akhilesh%20ji%2C%20don't%20give%20gyan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Thakur%20not%20getting%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20this%20time.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20he%20is%20agitated%20because%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20minister.%20I%20read%20pain%20on%20your%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20ended%20his%20address%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20took%20a%20parting%20shot%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20%26quot%3BThis%20government%20is%20not%20one%20that%20would%20run%2C%20it%20is%20a%20government%20that%20will%20topple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722334200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fue3ann2o_akhilesh-anurag-split_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-anurag-thakur-parliament-updates-akhilesh-yadav-vs-anurag-thakur-in-lok-sabha-over-agnipath-scheme-6222328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20debate%20on%20Budget%202024%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20saw%20an%20explosive%20exchange%20between%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20BJP%2