s%20not%20only%20techno-optimistic%2C%20but%20it%20also%20has%20a%20nostalgic%20vibe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20'We%20were%20great%2C%20we%20are%20great%2C%20and%20we%20can%20be%20great.'%20That's%20an%20empowering%20message%20to%20people%20who%20are%20building.%26quot%3B%20Or%20as%20Dick%20Lucas%2C%20a%20software%20developer%20who%20subscribes%20to%20Pirate%20Wires%2C%20put%20it%20to%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20I%20read%20the%20tech%20section%20of%20a%20news%20site%20when%20I%20can%20go%20to%20the%20tech%20publication%20that's%20in%20tech%20with%20the%20people%20that%20are%20doing%20the%20stuff%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELucas'%20bio%20on%20X%20is%20emblematic%20of%20much%20of%20the%20pro-tech%20media's%20audience%3A%20%26quot%3BTechno-optimist%2C%20American%20Dynamism%2C%20long%20Mars%2C%20long%20humanity%2C%20long%20crypto%2C%20long%20freedom%2C%20accelerate%20or%20die.%26quot%3B%20These%20readers%20tend%20to%20see%20themselves%2C%20as%20Lucas%20describes%20it%2C%20not%20as%20%26quot%3Btinfoil-hat%20guys%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bburn-it-down%20guys%26quot%3B%20but%20as%20rational%20but%20radical%20contrarians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20identity-driven%20brands%2C%20and%20their%20identities%20vary.%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20is%20like%20a%20cross%20between%20Joe%20Rogan%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20View%26quot%3B%3A%20fratty%2C%20barbed%2C%20gossipy.%20Coogan%20opts%20for%20an%20informed%20but%20breathless%20documentary-style%20approach.%20(Coogan%2C%20who%20is%20an%20entrepreneur%20in%20residence%20at%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20often%20receives%20comments%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do2VuPJ40yEw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20running%20ads%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20Meanwhile%2C%20Pirate%20Wires%20is%20urgent%20and%20irreverent%2C%20often%20veering%20into%20winding%20tangents%20that%20yield%20contradictory%20insights.%20A%20typical%20passage%3A%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20Kamala%20is%20running%20for%20president%20(don't%20ask%20how)%2C%20it%20was%20inevitable%20the%20press%20would%20pivot%20to%20publicity%20for%20Team%20Coconut.%20But%20with%20gaslighting%20so%20extreme%2C%20and%20months%20to%20go%20before%20the%20election%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20our%20entire%20world's%20about%20to%20be%20rewritten.%20Screenshot%20everything%2C%20and%20try%20to%20remember%20who%20you%20are.%26quot%3B%20As%20Stephens%20puts%20it%2C%20reading%20Pirate%20Wires%20feels%20%26quot%3Blike%20being%20inside%20Solana's%20brain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20the%20progenitors%20of%20these%20projects%20and%20their%20fans%20share%20an%20overarching%20ethos%20that%20building%20and%20turgidly%20celebrating%20tech%20is%20itself%20an%20identity.%20They%20also%20tend%20to%20share%20other%20aspects%20of%20their%20identities%3A%2070%25%20of%20Pirate%20Wires'%20paid%20subscribers%20are%20men%20ages%2025%20to%2040%20who%20work%20in%20tech%20and%20finance.%20In%20his%20own%20words%2C%20Solana%20is%20writing%20for%20and%20perpetuating%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20class%20of%20people%20building%20new%20things%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20isolated%20from%20mainstream%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20aim%20of%20the%20pro-tech%20media%20is%20to%20crystallize%20and%20propel%20an%20unapologetic%2C%20unified%20bloc%20of%20people%20working%20toward%20a%20shared%20vision%20of%20tech%3A%20Us.%20The%20other%20is%20to%20identify%2C%20call%20out%2C%20and%20neutralize%20its%20detractors%3A%20Them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20weird%20that%20tech%20people%20have%20been%20painted%20as%20the%20villains%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Packy%20McCormick%2C%20whose%20techno-optimistic%20Substack%2C%20Not%20Boring%2C%20has%20some%20225%2C000%20subscribers.%20Pro-tech%20media%20outlets%2C%20he%20says%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Breframing%20who%20the%20villains%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20and%20its%20perceived%20anti-tech%20bias%20are%20frequently%20in%20the%20pro-tech%20media's%20crosshairs%2C%20from%20entire%20publications%20like%20The%20Washington%20Post%20and%20TechCrunch%20to%20individual%20tech%20journalists%20like%20Taylor%20Lorenz%2C%20Ryan%20Mac%2C%20and%20Kevin%20Roose.%20Pirate%20Wires%20has%20published%20two%20particularly%20acerbic%20stories%20%E2%80%94%20one%20by%20Solana%2C%20one%20by%20the%20journalist%20Jesse%20Singal%20%E2%80%94%20criticizing%20one%20story%20by%20the%20journalist%20Casey%20Newton%20that%20they%20argued%20wildly%20overplayed%20the%20rise%20of%20Nazis%20on%20Substack.%20%26quot%3BCasey%20isn't%20a%20journalist%2C%26quot%3B%20Solana%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BCasey%20is%20a%20political%20activist%20who%20calls%20himself%20a%20journalist%20in%20service%20of%20mainstreaming%20his%20activism%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20neutrality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20kind%20of%20writing%20needs%20a%20counterpoint%2C%20and%20it%20just%20never%20had%20one%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Solana%20tells%20me%20of%20the%20Newton%20articles.%20(Newton%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTech%20was%20held%20accountable%20by%20legacy%20media%2C%20and%20now%20Pirate%20Wires%20is%20holding%20legacy%20media%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Erik%20Torenberg%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20pro-tech%20company%20Turpentine%20Media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pro-tech%20media's%20other%20adversaries%20are%20a%20constellation%20of%20government%2C%20corporate%2C%20and%20entertainment%20figures%20dubbed%20too%20reflexively%20anti-tech%2C%20too%20anti-growth%2C%20or%20too%20politically%20correct.%20On%20Pirate%20Wires%2C%20jeremiads%20have%20been%20written%20against%20Anthony%20Fauci%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Boversaw%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20erosions%20of%20institutional%20trust%20in%20American%20history%26quot%3B%3B%20Ellen%20Pao%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20architect%20of%20tech's%20%23metoo%20movement%26quot%3B%3B%20DEI%20activists%20at%20Google%3B%20DEI%20at%20large%3B%20Disney%2C%20for%20its%20penchant%20for%20%26quot%3Bgirlboss%20protagonists%26quot%3B%3B%20and%20NPR's%20CEO%2C%20Katherine%20Maher%2C%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bnear%20perfect%20record%20of%20ideological%20opposition%20to%20Silicon%20Valley.%26quot%3B%20Though%20Solana%20has%20since%20moved%20to%20Miami%2C%20his%20fiercest%20ire%20on%20Pirate%20Wires%20remains%20fixed%20on%20San%20Francisco's%20liberal%20politicians.%20A%20sampling%20of%20recent%20headlines%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20San%20Francisco%20Attracts%20and%20Traps%20Homeless%20Transplants%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHow%20San%20Francisco's%20DEI%20Industrial%20Complex%20Works%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BInside%20SF%20Public%20Schools'%20Shocking%20Health%20Curriculum.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20has%20similarly%20taken%20aim%20at%20figures%20including%20Fauci%2C%20George%20Soros%2C%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20California%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20when%20David%20Sacks%20was%20personally%20bankrolling%20the%20recall%20of%20the%20San%20Francisco%20district%20attorney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchesa-boudin-san-francisco-da-recall-election-live-results-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChesa%20Boudin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20and%20the%20other%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20hosts%20goaded%20listeners%20to%20support%20recalling%20Boudin%20and%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%20in%20exchange%20for%20personal%20shout-outs%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmboldened%20by%20this%20chorus%20of%20combativeness%2C%20many%20of%20the%20pro-tech%20media's%20luminaries%20and%20disciples%20are%20taking%20its%20agenda%20into%20the%20real%20world.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20belief%20and%20you%20see%20it%20in%20Pirate%20Wires%2C%20maybe%20you%20can%20bring%20it%20up%20at%20your%20company's%20all-hands%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Coogan%20says.%20Or%20if%20you're%20management%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20pro-tech%20media%20to%20tell%20your%20underlings%20to%20get%20with%20the%20program.%20In%20November%202022%2C%20a%20week%20after%20Elon%20Musk%20took%20over%20Twitter%20and%20laid%20off%20half%20its%20staff%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20encouraged%20concerned%20remaining%20staffers%20to%20listen%20to%20%26quot%3BAll-In.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20recent%20podcast%20covers%20the%20current%20layoffs%20happening%20across%20tech%20and%20provides%20some%20insight%20into%20why%20this%20is%20happening%2Fnecessary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20VP%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20reporting%20from%20Casey%20Newton.%20Or%20you%20can%20take%20the%20pro-tech%20media%20to%20city%20hall.%20At%20a%20recent%20meeting%20of%20San%20Francisco's%20board%20of%20supervisors%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmicsolana%2Fstatus%2F1729301433877405864%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewoman%3C%2Fa%3E%20lambasted%20a%20city%20initiative%20that%20redistributed%20%24120%20million%20in%20police%20funding%20to%20Black%20communities%20by%20citing%20a%20lengthy%20quote%20from%20a%20Pirate%20Wires%20screed%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20racial%20equity%20cash%20grab.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20significantly%2C%20the%20pro-tech%20media%20has%20begun%20to%20influence%20the%20national%20political%20agenda.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20hosts%20Palihapitiya%20and%20Sacks%20hosted%20an%20up-to-%24300%2C000-a-head%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-donald-trump-fundraiser-presidential-campaign-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efundraiser%20for%20Trump's%20reelection%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Sacks'%20%2420%20million%20home%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20an%20event%20that%20once%20would%20have%20been%20unimaginable%20in%20the%20city.%20Trump%20went%20on%20to%20be%20treated%20to%20a%20fawning%20interview%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20and%20Sacks%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%2C%20where%20the%20Peter%20Thiel%20protege%20JD%20Vance%20was%20named%20Trump's%20pick%20for%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20members%20of%20the%20news%20media%20I%20talked%20to%20about%20pro-tech%20media%2C%20some%20were%20backhandedly%20laudatory.%20%26quot%3BMike%20Solana%20is%20a%20talented%20guy%20on%20a%20number%20of%20levels%2C%20some%20of%20them%20nefarious%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Merchant%2C%20a%20tech%20columnist%20who%20wrote%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BBlood%20in%20the%20Machine%3A%20The%20Origins%20of%20the%20Rebellion%20Against%20Big%20Tech%2C%26quot%3B%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20in%20politically%20playing%20the%20game%20to%20get%20funding%20for%20his%20projects%20and%20also%20in%20being%20an%20effective%20asshole%20writer%20who%20can%20get%20attention%20on%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%20Others%20exhibited%20the%20same%20instinct%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20direct%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20audiences%20as%20tech%20entrepreneurs.%20When%20I%20asked%20the%20Semafor%20founder%20Ben%20Smith%20for%20an%20interview%2C%20he%20wrote%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BSuper%20interesting%20topic%20but%20I'd%20rather%20compete%20with%20you%20on%20this%20one%20than%20be%20a%20pundit.%20%3A)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20radio%20tower%20with%20signals%20that%20are%20shaped%20as%20quote%20bubbles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a7fc0aaab37011780b7c3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmboldened%20by%20this%20chorus%20of%20combativeness%2C%20many%20of%20the%20pro-tech%20media's%20luminaries%20and%20disciples%20are%20taking%20its%20agenda%20into%20the%20real%20world.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20were%20cautiously%20enthusiastic.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20journalists%20own%20the%20ethical%20obligation%20of%20informing%20people%20about%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric%20Newcomer%2C%20a%20reporter%20who%20left%20Bloomberg%20in%202020%20to%20start%20a%20Substack%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20%26quot%3BTech%20is%20oriented%20in%20a%20good%20way%20around%20productive%20solutions%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20media%20they've%20just%20been%20whining%20and%20abrogating%20responsibility.%20So%20if%20these%20people%20say%20'We%20can%20do%20news%20better%2C'%20well%2C%20good.%20Let%20them%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20early%20pro-tech%20media%20ventures%20have%20already%20figured%20out%20that%20even%20the%20most%20avid%20enthusiasts%20will%20retreat%20from%20bland%20propaganda%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20sleekly%20packaged.%20Andreessen%20Horowitz's%20publication%20Future%2C%20for%20example%2C%20launched%20in%202021%20with%20a%20string%20of%20high-profile%20editorial%20hires%20and%20a%20glitzy%20website%20touting%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20future%20of%20media.%26quot%3B%20It%20failed%20to%20gain%20a%20loyal%20readership%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa16z-future-closes-staff-exit-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20just%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20with%20monied%20backers%2C%20high-profile%20connections%2C%20and%20a%20bravado%20that%20captures%20the%20tech%20industry's%20zeitgeist%2C%20building%20a%20successful%20media%20company%20in%202024%20is%20a%20steep%20challenge.%20Media's%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20model%20is%20just%20completely%20fucked%2C%26quot%3B%20Solana%20says.%20As%20advertising%20dollars%20dry%20up%20for%20publishers%2C%20he's%20been%20toying%20with%20different%20strategies%20for%20monetization.%20Still%2C%20Pirate%20Wires'%20%2420-a-month%20subscription%20fee%20is%20a%20steep%20price%20for%20what%20subscribers%20get%3A%20The%20site%20tends%20to%20stagnate%2C%20with%20several%20days%20often%20passing%20between%20single%20posts.%20Solana%20still%20assigns%2C%20edits%2C%20and%20writes%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20site's%20content.%20%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20I%20have%20two%20full-time%20jobs%20right%20now%20and%20it's%20absolutely%20miserable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Perhaps%20tellingly%2C%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20leave%20Founders%20Fund%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20as%20mistrust%20in%20traditional%20media%20remains%20high%20and%20readers%20flock%20to%20more%20identity-focused%20brands%2C%20these%20projects%20will%20likely%20only%20gain%20traction%20and%20play%20an%20increasingly%20important%20role%20in%20shaping%20how%20the%20tech%20industry%20sees%20itself%20and%20perceives%20its%20enemies.%20Lulu%20Cheng%20Meservey%2C%20a%20communications%20expert%20who%20has%20worked%20extensively%20with%20tech%20founders%2C%20told%20me%20that%20when%20she%20talks%20to%20entrepreneurs%20about%20the%20publications%20they'd%20most%20like%20to%20be%20covered%20in%20these%20days%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20will%20usually%20say%20The%20Information%20and%20Bloomberg%2C%20but%20also%20Pirate%20Wires%20or%20John%20Coogan.%26quot%3B%20More%20and%20more%2C%20tech's%20elite%20are%20following%20Balaji%20Srinivasan's%20advice%20in%20a%20recent%20Pirate%20Wires%20interview%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BDon't%20fucking%20talk%20to%20journalists%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20going%20to%20the%20pro-tech%20media%20to%20set%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20their%20success%20comes%20with%20an%20irony%3A%20The%20more%20they%20multiply%2C%20the%20more%20they're%20starting%20to%20act%20like%20the%20media%20outlets%20they%20despise%2C%20shamelessly%20vying%20for%20attention%20and%20an%20edge%20in%20branding.%20On%20June%2030%2C%20Solana%20posted%20a%203%2C000-word%20essay%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20the%20Media%20Now%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20a%20new%20target%3A%20his%20rising%20competition%20in%20the%20pro-tech%20media.%20He%20took%20on%20an%20uncharacteristically%20defensive%20tone%20listing%20Pirate%20Wires'%20bona%20fides%20against%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20field%3