2%26quot%3BFor%20How%20Many%20Years...%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Raps%20Centre%20Over%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20Dues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Centre%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20any%20decision%20for%20years%20on%20the%20pension%20payable%20to%20retired%20regular%20captains%20of%20the%20Army%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20(OROP)%20scheme%20and%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20R%20Mahadevan%20gave%20one%20last%20opportunity%20to%20the%20Centre%20till%20November%2014%20for%20resolving%20the%20anomalies%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20pension%20of%20such%20retired%20officers%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20shall%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20welfare%20funds%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20warned%20the%20government%20that%20if%20the%20decision%20is%20not%20taken%20by%20November%2014%2C%20it%20will%20direct%20for%20enhanced%20pension%20by%2010%20per%20cent%20to%20the%20retired%20regular%20captains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20November%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20in%20the%20court%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Centre%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhatti%20said%20six%20anomalies%20have%20been%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Kochi%20bench%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal%20(AFT)%2C%20which%20need%20to%20be%20rectified%2C%20but%20the%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20how%20many%20years%20will%20this%20go%20on%3F%20Either%20you%20pay%20an%20enhanced%20pension%20by%2010%20per%20cent%20or%20we%20are%20imposing%20a%20cost%20on%20you.%20We%20wanted%20a%20decision%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20but%20you%20have%20not%20taken%20it.%20This%20matter%20came%20up%20in%202021%20but%20still%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken.%26quot%3B%20Bhatti%20said%20the%20government%20cannot%20take%20a%20piecemeal%20decision%2C%20it%20has%20to%20look%20at%20the%20issue%20holistically%20and%20consider%20all%20the%20six%20anomalies%20as%20the%20decision%20may%20affect%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20do%20is%20tender%20my%20apology.%20Please%20give%20us%20one%20more%20chance%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20in%20this%20regard.%20We%20will%20file%20an%20affidavit%20in%20this%20regard.%20Give%20us%20three%20months'%20time%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20initially%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20further%20time%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20accept%20any%20affidavit%20and%20said%20it%20will%20direct%20an%20enhanced%20pension%20to%20these%20retired%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20this%3F%20If%20the%20government%20is%20not%20taking%20a%20decision%2C%20I%20cannot%20do%20anything.%20This%20does%20not%20give%20solace%20to%20these%20officers.%20They%20are%20retired%20captains.%20They%20have%20no%20say.%20They%20have%20no%20access%20to%20you%20people.%20Either%20you%20start%20paying%2010%20per%20cent%20more%20or%20pay%20the%20cost.%20The%20choice%20is%20yours.%26quot%3B%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20bench%20started%20dictating%20the%20order%20for%20enhanced%20pension%20for%20the%20retired%20captains%2C%20Bhatti%20asked%20it%20to%20kindly%20impose%20a%20cost%20because%20that%20will%20serve%20equity%20better%20than%20enhanced%20pension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20gave%20time%20till%20November%2014%20to%20the%20government%20as%20a%20last%20opportunity%20but%20imposed%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20on%20it%2C%20saying%20the%20amount%20has%20to%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20welfare%20fund%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2023%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20the%20regional%20bench%20of%20the%20AFT%20had%20passed%20an%20order%20on%20December%207%2C%202021%20according%20to%20which%20the%20government%20was%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20pension%20payable%20to%20the%20retired%20regular%20captains%2C%20noticing%20that%20there%20was%20an%20anomaly%20that%20required%20to%20be%20resolved%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20OROP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20challenged%20the%20AFT%20order%20and%20arrayed%2013%20retired%20regular%20captains%20as%20a%20party%20to%20the%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20this%20court%20has%20repeatedly%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20to%20enable%20the%20appellant%20government%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20pension%20of%20the%20retired%20regular%20captains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20we%20are%20inclined%20to%20impose%20exemplary%20costs%20and%20also%20direct%20that%20the%20regular%20captains%20will%20get%20pension%20enhanced%20by%2020%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20date%20the%20OROP%20scheme%20is%20applicable.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20last%20opportunity%20to%20enable%20the%20appellant%20to%20obtain%20instructions%2C%20re-list%20on%20July%2030%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20in%20its%20July%2023%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20of%20the%20dispute%20lies%20in%20the%20OROP%20scheme%20introduced%20by%20the%20Centre%20in%202015.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20pensions%20for%20past%20retirees%20were%20fixed%20at%20par%20with%20that%20for%20the%20current%20retirees%20of%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20certain%20anomalies%20crept%20in%20the%20pension%20tables%20for%20captains%20and%20majors%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20data%20of%20the%20officers%20in%20the%20ranks%20of%20regular%20captains%20and%20majors%20since%20the%20minimum%20current%20rank%20of%20retirement%20to%20attain%20pensionable%20service%20is%20lieutenant%20colonel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20appointed%20a%20One%20Man%20Judicial%20Committee%20(OMJC)%20to%20recommend%20the%20resolution%20of%20this%20anomaly%20in%202016%20but%20no%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20ministry%20on%20the%20matter%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Kochi%20Bench%20of%20the%20AFT%20directed%20the%20ministry%20to%20resolve%20the%20anomaly%20based%20on%20the%20OMJC's%20recommendations%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Centre%20challenged%20the%20AFT%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722328980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fef9ofil8_supreme-court-generic_625x300_30_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-how-many-years-court-raps-centre-over-one-rank-one-pension-orop-dues-6221801%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Centre%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20any%20decision%20for%20years%20on%20the%20pension%20payable%20to%20retired%20regular%20captains%20of%20the%20Army%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20(OROP)%20scheme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-how-many-years-court-raps-centre-over-one-rank-one-pension-orop-dues-6221801%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-how-many-years-court-raps-centre-over-one-rank-one-pension-orop-dues-6221801%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-how-many-years-court-raps-centre-over-one-rank-one-pension-orop-dues-6221801%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%