20Takes%20Dig%20At%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Uncle%2C%20Gets%20A%20%26quot%3BDeputy%26quot%3B%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20swipe%20at%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20uncle%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20drew%20a%20sharp%20counter%20in%20the%20Assembly%20this%20morning.%C2%A0At%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20address%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20congratulated%20Samajwadi%20Party%20veteran%20Mata%20Prasad%20Pandey%2C%20who%20has%20replaced%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20after%20the%20party%20chief%20was%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Kannauj%20in%20this%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Mr%20Pandey%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20served%20twice%20as%20the%20Speaker%20of%20this%20House.%20I%20congratulate%20you%20on%20your%20selection.%20It's%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20you%20tricked%20chacha%20(uncle).%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20was%20referring%20to%20Shivpal%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20uncle%2C%20who%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20Mr%20Pandey.%C2%A0%26quot%3BChacha%20always%20gets%20tricked%20like%20this.%20This%20is%20his%20destiny%20because%20the%20nephew%20is%20always%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20was%20seen%20smiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20leader%20waited%20for%20his%20turn.%20When%20he%20rose%20to%20speak%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20tricked%2C%20Pandey%20ji%20is%20very%20senior.%26quot%3B%20Addressing%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20you%20for%20three%20years.%20You%20tricked%20me%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20MLAs%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20burst%20into%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivpal%20Yadav%20then%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP's%20lack-lustre%20show%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20this%20election.%20%26quot%3BYou%20tricked%20me%2C%20you%20lagged%20behind%20in%20this%20election%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20stormed%20ahead.%20Mark%20my%20words%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20will%20come%20to%20power%20in%20the%202027%20(state%20polls)%20and%20your%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20trick%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seasoned%20leader's%20remarks%20came%20amid%20friction%20within%20the%20state%20BJP.%20In%20a%20show%20of%20united%20front%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20flanked%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Maurya%20and%20Brajesh%20Pathak%20when%20he%20addressed%20the%20media%20before%20the%20Assembly%20session%20began%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20brother%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20founder%2C%20the%20late%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MLA%20for%20nearly%20three%20decades%20now.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20a%20state%20minister%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20He%20is%20now%20the%20National%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202017%2C%20when%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20coming%20of%20age%20politically%20and%20taking%20charge%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20founded%20the%20Pragatisheel%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20In%202022%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20cleared%20his%20differences%20with%20nephew%20Akhilesh%2C%20rejoined%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20merged%20his%20party%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722326100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1mpo4bio_yogi-shivpal_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-shivpal-yadav-akhilesh-yadav-yogi-adityanath-takes-dig-at-akhilesh-yadavs-uncle-gets-a-deputy-reply-6221279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20swipe%20a