20coordination%20with%20the%20state%20government.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20primary%20thing%20is%20to%20recover%20the%20bodies%20and%20save%20those%20who%20can%20be%20saved%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%20said%20that%20a%20control%20room%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20provide%20immediate%20relief%20and%20rescue%20assistance%20following%20the%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20affected%20areas%20are%20Mundakkai%2C%20Chooralmala%2C%20Attamala%20and%20Noolpuzha%2C%20authorities%20have%20said.%20Many%20roads%20have%20collapsed%20and%20a%20bridge%20has%20been%20swept%20away%20and%20several%20areas%20have%20become%20unreachable%2C%20Health%20Minister%20Veena%20George%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20re-establish%20the%20connectivity.%20Helicopters%20will%20also%20be%20brought%20in%2C%20but%20the%20weather%20is%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722326040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frq4p3m5o_wayanad_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-landslides-that-killed-54-triggered-by-record-372mm-rain-in-24-hours-6221398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2054%20people%20have%20died%20after%20massive%20landslides%20hit%20the%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20Wayanad%20district%20in%20Kerala%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-landslides-that-killed-54-triggered-by-record-372mm-rain-in-24-hours-6221398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-landslides-that-killed-54-triggered-by-record-372mm-rain-in-24-hours-6221398%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-landslides-that-killed-54-triggered-by-record-372mm-rain-in-24-hours-6221398%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B