2C%20and%20hospitals.%20Subsequent%20patches%20by%20Microsoft%20and%20CrowdStrike%20resolved%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20not%20before%20hackers%20exploited%20the%20outage.%20India's%20CERT-In%20warned%20companies%20of%20phishing%20campaigns%20and%20malware%20related%20to%20this%20incident%2C%20sharing%2025%20URLs%20to%20block.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fmicrosoft-outage-government-asks-companies-to-block-these-25-dangerous-urls-full-list%2Farticleshow%2F112130794.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Proposes%20Life%20Term%20In%20'Love%20Jihad'%20Law.%20How%20BJP%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20Reacted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Yogi%20Adityanth-led%20government%20has%20introduced%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20which%20proposes%20harsher%20punishment%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20in%20'love%20jihad'%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20amendments%20have%20been%20welcomed%20by%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20while%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20termed%20it%20a%20'divisive'%20move%2C%20aimed%20at%20creating%20'animosity'%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20who%20reached%20the%20Assembly%2C%20this%20morning%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20legislation%20should%20be%20welcomed%20as%20this%20would%20act%20as%20a%20'deterrent'%20against%20such%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Mohsin%20Raza%20said%20that%20the%20law%2C%20when%20amended%2C%20will%20help%20greatly%20in%20tackling%20illegal%20religious%20conversions%20as%20many%20'love%20jihad'%20cases%20have%20emerged%20where%20impersonators%20marry%20a%20girl%20by%20hiding%20their%20identity%20and%20then%20force%20her%20to%20convert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20impersonator%20plays%20with%20the%20life%20of%20your%20daughter%2C%20why%20shouldn't%20the%20culprit%20be%20held%20accountable%3F%20If%20an%20imposter%20marries%20any%20girl%20by%20hiding%20his%20identity%20and%20with%20malicious%20intent%2C%20why%20can't%20such%20people%20be%20brought%20to%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20slammed%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20for%20brining%20amendments%20in%20the%20existing%20laws%20regarding%20'love%20jihad'%20and%20said%20that%20it%20nothing%20but%20negative%20politics%20and%20motivated%20by%20the%20BJP's%20'aversion'%20towards%20a%20particular%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Fakhrul%20Hasan%20Chand%20in%20a%20video%20message%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUP%20has%20already%20a%20law%20on%20love%20jihad.%20If%20someone%20traps%20someone%20in%20his%2Fher%20love%20trap%20with%20some%20motive%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20law%20for%20it%20but%20the%20BJP%20only%20wants%20to%20do%20negative%20politics.%20It%20does%20not%20want%20to%20do%20anything%20about%20unemployment%20and%20paper%20leak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20BJP%20leader%20Mohsin%20Raza%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20for%20'smelling%20a%20conspiracy'%20in%20the%20proposed%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20strict%20regulation%20is%20required%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20such%20practises.%20The%20BJP%20believes%20in%20'sabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikas.'%20It's%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Opposition%20finds%20it%20communal%20and%20discriminatory.%20Their%20opposition%20to%20the%20ordinance%20is%20driven%20by%20their%20appeasement%20policy%20towards%20a%20certain%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohsin%20Raza%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20existing%20law%2C%20the%20punishment%20for%20such%20cases%20of%20an%20imposter%20marrying%20so