dorable-rose-print%2Fphotostory%2F112100471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20An%20Entire%2023%20Member%20Sri%20Lankan%20Handball%20Team%20Vanished%20In%20Germany%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202004%2C%20an%20extraordinary%20incident%20unfolded%20in%20Bavaria%2C%20Germany.%20A%2023-man%20Sri%20Lankan%20handball%20team%20had%20arrived%20in%20the%20country%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20sports%20exchange%20programme%20consisting%20of%20friendly%20matches%20against%20local%20clubs%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsri-lankans-pull-off-disappearing-act-in-bavaria%2Fa-1332926%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeutsche%20Welle.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20the%20team's%20performance%20during%20a%20match%20raised%20eyebrows.%20Players%20seemed%20to%20show%20very%20unfamiliarity%20with%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20sport%2C%20and%20their%20performance%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bawful%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20opposing%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20unthinkable%20happened%20the%20next%20morning.%20The%20whole%20Sri%20Lankan%20delegation%20of%2016%20players%20and%20nine%20other%20members%2C%20including%20the%20coach%2C%20vanished%20into%20thin%20air.%20Initially%2C%20their%20hosts%20thought%20the%20team%20members%20got%20lost%2C%20but%20a%20search%20in%20the%20rooms%20told%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20left%20all%20their%20personal%20belongings%20behind%2C%20including%20sports%20equipment%20and%20team%20jerseys%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20thank-you%20note%20for%20local%20sports%20authorities%20showing%20appreciation%20for%20the%20extended%20hospitality%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20were%20leaving%20for%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20authorities%20were%20baffled%20by%20the%20sudden%20disappearance%20of%20the%20entire%20national%20handball%20team.%20The%20incident%20remains%20a%20perplexing%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Sports%20Exchange%20Programme%20organiser%20Dietmer%20Doering%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fsouth_asia%2F3658966.stm%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ethe%20BBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20initially%20thought%20the%20team%20had%20gotten%20lost%20in%20nearby%20woods%20while%20jogging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20a%20note%20had%20been%20found%20saying%20the%2023-strong%20team%20had%20gone%20to%20France.%20%26quot%3BWe%20now%20know%20they%20crossed%20into%20Italy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Doering%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20even%20left%20their%20dirty%20laundry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doering%20told%20Priyath%20Liyanage%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20Sinhala%20service%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20organisers%20were%20feeling%20extremely%20let%20down%20by%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20last%20time%20we%20will%20be%20doing%20this.%20I%20am%20not%20planning%20to%20invite%20any%20more%20teams%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20team%20of%2023%20men%2C%20including%20the%20coach%20and%20the%20manager%2C%20has%20taken%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handball%20team%20was%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20programme%20in%20which%20teams%20from%20both%20countries%20visited%20each%20other%20for%20friendly%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20ministry%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20said%20the%20trip%20was%20not%20authorised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Sri%20Lankan%20National%20Handball%20Team%20Existed%20in%202004%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fsouth_asia%2F3658966.stm%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ethe%20BBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ministry%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20handball%20is%20a%20sport%20very%20rarely%20played%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20national%20team%20was%20a%20mystery.%20The%20performance%20of%20the%20team%20had%20been%20poor%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsri-lankans-pull-off-disappearing-act-in-bavaria%2Fa-1332926%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeutsche%20Welle%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20German%20and%20Italian%20authorities%20scratch%20their%20heads%20about%20the%20best%20way%20out%20of%20the%20mess%2C%20reports%20say%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20officials%20have%20confirmed%20that%20the%20country%20doesn't%20even%20have%20a%20national%20handball%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20this%20intriguing%20case%20of%20the%20missing%20Sri%20Lankan%20handball%20team%20inspired%20an%20Italian-Sri%20Lankan%20comedy%20movie%2C%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3BMachan%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewritten%2C%20directed%2C%20and%20produced%20by%20Uberto%20Pasolini%20and%20released%20in%20the%20year%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722320820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9i2nd9p8_machan_625x300_30_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fhow-an-entire-23-member-sri-lankan-handball-team-vanished-without-a-trace-in-germany-6220499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20September%202004%2C%20a%2023-member%20Sri%20Lankan%20handball%20team%20mysteriously%20vanished%20during%20a%20sports%20exchange%20program%20in%20Bavaria%2C%20Germany.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fhow-an-entire-23-member-sri-lankan-handball-team-vanished-without-a-trace-in-germany-6220499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fhow-an-entire-23-member-sri-lankan-handball-team-vanished-without-a-trace-in-germany-6220499%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fhow-an-entire-23-member-sri-lankan-handball-team-vanished-without-a-trace-in-germany-6220499%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title