C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20me%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rachna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Foundation%20(AKF)%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20with%20Project%20Lehar.%20Started%20to%20provide%20vocational%20training%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20life%20skills%20courses%20to%20marginalised%20young%20women%2C%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20run%20by%20AKF%20in%20partnership%20with%20The%20King%E2%80%99s%20Trust%20International%2C%20empowers%20girls%20and%20young%20women%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20to%20rediscover%20and%20realise%20their%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Project%20Lehar%20team%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290617%2Fsonal-shukla-educated-girls-mumbai-slums-feminist-icon-women-movement-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaching%20out%20to%20help%20school%20dropouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Risia%20block%20restart%20their%20education.%20This%20was%20a%20godsend%20opportunity%20for%20Rachna%20to%20not%20just%20resume%20her%20studies%20but%20also%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20to%20drop%20her%20marriage%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20was%20admitted%20into%20college%20through%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20she%20was%20also%20counseled%20on%20entrepreneurial%20and%20career%20prospects.%20One%20such%20session%20on%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20was%20to%20change%20her%20life%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWheat%20stalk%20painting%2C%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20is%20a%20laborious%20and%20time%20consuming%20process.%20It%20is%20created%20by%20cutting%20wheat%20stalks%20into%20fine%20sections%20to%20craft%20intricate%20designs%20on%20cloth%20using%20sharp-edged%20blades%20and%20razors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A