%22title%22%3A%22Started%20With%20Few%20Jars%20on%20The%20Roadside%2C%20How%20a%20Homemaker%20Built%20Her%20Pickle%20Empire%20Earning%20Rs%205%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Krishna%20Yadav%20stood%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20holding%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20for%20Diversified%20Agriculture.%20Her%20entire%20life%20journey%20flashed%20before%20her%20eyes%20as%20she%20gazed%20at%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Daulatpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Krishna%20never%20attended%20school.%20After%20her%20marriage%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Bulandshahr%2C%20where%20she%20faced%20a%20dire%20situation%20when%20her%20husband%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20traffic%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLater%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20start%20a%20vehicle%20trading%20business%2C%20but%20we%20incurred%20huge%20losses.%20We%20had%20to%20sell%20our%20two%20houses%2C%20each%20spread%20across%20150%20%3Cem%3Egaj%20%3C%2Fem%3E(approximately%201%2C300%20sqft).%20It%20became%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20survive.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20eat%20vegetables%20anymore%20and%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(salt%20and%20flatbread)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20With%20only%20Rs%20500%20in%20her%20pocket%2C%20she%20relocated%20to%20the%20city%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20looked%20for%20jobs%2C%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20education%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20work.%20My%20husband%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20employment.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20we%20began%20working%20on%20a%20field%20through%20sharecropping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharecropping%20is%20a%20legal%20arrangement%20where%20a%20landowner%20permits%20a%20tenant%20to%20cultivate%20their%20land%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20crops%20produced.%20The%20five-member%20family%20began%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20the%20field.%20They%20spent%20their%20days%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20but%20the%20income%20from%20their%20efforts%20was%20insufficient%20to%20sustain%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20of%20vegetables%20in%20the%20market%20would%20fluctuate%20and%20we%20would%20hardly%20earn%20any%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starting%20with%20karonda%20(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20Krishna%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20she%20heard%20about%20a%20training%20programme%20on%20value%20addition%20of%20post-harvest%20losses%20through%20a%20television%20programme.%20She%20enrolled%20in%20a%20course%20at%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20where%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAmit%2520tells%2520The%2520Better%2520India%2Ctastes%2520it%2520becomes%2520a%2520fan.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emastered%20the%20art%20and%20science%20of%20making%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurabba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marmalade).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20path%20for%20her%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%20500%20to%20Rs%205%20crore%20empire%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20an%20enthused%20student%2C%20Krishna%20would%20set%20out%20to%20the%20training%20centre%20with%20post-harvest%20losses%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%20from%20her%20field%2C%20a%20few%20spices%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20my%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmothers)%20make%20pickles%2C%20the%20know-how%20that%20I%20learnt%20in%20the%20training%20was%20insightful.%20As%20homemakers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20calculate%20the%20amounts%20of%20spices%20and%20salt%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20pickle.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20taste%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20pickles%20naturally.%20The%20key%20was%20the%20measurement%20of%20spices%20and%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Krishna%20started%20making%20the%20pickles%2C%20but%20she%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20commercialising%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20small%20table%20on%20the%20roadside%20and%20put%20our%20products%20on%20display.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20very%20busy%20road%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20attract%20people%20to%20our%20stall.%20So%2C%20we%20placed%20two%20large%20earthen%20pots%20of%20water%20along%20with%20the%20pickles.%20I%20offered%20pickles%20as%20samples%20to%20those%20who%20stopped%20to%20drink%20free%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20simple%20yet%20effective%20strategy%20slowly%20built%20her%20customer%20base.%20She%20also%20started%20participating%20in%20local%20fairs%20to%20promote%20the%20products.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20her%20pickles%20grew%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20formally%20launch%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20eventually%20open%20her%20own%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20Today%2C%20she%20offers%20over%20250%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300822%2Fsenior-citizen-entrepreneur-sheila-pickles-jams-traditional-kerala-recipes-home-business-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20herbal%20juices%2C%20chutneys%2C%20marmalades%2C%20and%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Rohilla%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20pickles%20perfectly%20capture%20the%20essence%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20goodness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offering%20a%20nostalgic%20taste.%20Their%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20caters%20to%20every%20palate%20and%20mood.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20one%20of%20their%20jars%2C%20it%20bursts%20with%20authentic%20tastes%20and%20aromas%2C%20enhancing%20my%20simple%20meals.%20These%20pickles%20never%20disappoint%2C%20consistently%20maintaining%20their%20taste%20and%20quality%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20has%20established%20a%20five-storey%20facility%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20manufactures%2010%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20pickles%20daily%2C%20and%20her%20company%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20extraordinary%20determination%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20she%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20multiple%20awards%20including%20the%20Outstanding%20Women%20Award%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%202012%3B%20the%20Innovative%20Award%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20allied%20activities%20during%20the%20Global%20Agriculture%20Summit%202013%3B%20and%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Award%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20homemaker%20and%20my%20core%20job%20was%20to%20look%20after%20the%20household%20duties.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%20income%20in%20our%20dire%20times.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20my%20children%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20our%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20and%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20eldest%20son%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20while%20her%20other%20two%20children%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20both%20%3Cem%3Egaadi%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20car%20and%20a%20bungalow)%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20dignity%20to%20walk%20with%20pride.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20on%20television%2C%20and%20that%20dream%20came%20true%20with%20my%20business.%20However%2C%20achieving%20this%20success%20required%20consistent%20hard%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20stop%20now%2C%20I%20would%20risk%20losing%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20example%2C%20Krishna%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20adversity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20by%20failures.%20Do%20not%20view%20helplessness%20or%20failure%20as%20a%20setback%20but%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20greater%20achievements.%20If%20one%20door%20closes%2C%20many%20others%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722240366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Krishna%20Yadav%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20began%20selling%20pickles%20on%20the%20roadside.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20established%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20her%20business%20into%20a%20successful%20enterprise%20with%20over%20250%20varieties%20of%20products%20and%20a%20five-storey%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358846%2Futtar-pradesh-krishna-yadav-pickle-business-delhi-earn-crores-woman-empowerment%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Built%20By%2090%20People%20From%2018%20Countries%2C%20%E2%80%98Fairytale%E2%80%99%20Home%20in%20Rishikesh%20Was%20Made%20to%20Escape%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20replica%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20Raghav%20Kumar%20(30)%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20brother%20duo%20that%20has%20conceptualised%20a%20600-sq%20ft%20beauty%20in%20the%20heartland%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand.%20As%20fans%20of%20the%20seven-part%20fantasy%20series%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20will%20immediately%20guess%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20eight-foot-tall%20giant%20Rubeus%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20cabin%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20The%20Forbidden%20Forest%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20wood%20filled%20with%20wizarding%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosy%20fires%2C%20larger-than-life%20teacups%2C%20and%20a%20drooling%20boarhound%20Fang%20filled%20most%20evenings%20that%20Harry%20and%20his%20friends%20spent%20at%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s.%20I%20often%20found%20myself%20craving%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wish%20might%20just%20have%20been%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20and%20Ansh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%E2%80%99%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal%20that%20backed%20their%20transition%20from%20their%20city%20life%20in%20Delhi%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%202021.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20architects%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20(27)%20were%20keen%20on%20living%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20life%20closer%20to%20nature%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20they%20felt%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20achieved%20by%20being%20a%20part%20of%20modern%20corporate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247572%2Fmaharashtra-ecofriendly-green-architecture-domes-arches-cost-effective-sustainable-homes-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prized%20demand%20over%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20labour%20involved%20in%20these%20projects.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20greenwashing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghav%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20boys%20had%20their%20week%20cut%20out%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20weekdays%20spent%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20weekends%20trekking%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9_3aPdHLQ9Y%3Fsi%3DuSBCfoXQnBlYuCgm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20for%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20was%20sown%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%20trek%20to%20Rishikesh%20in%20December%202020%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20found%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20mountains%20and%20not%20return%20to%20the%20monotonous%20hustle.%20And%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20completely%20bewildered%20by%20topics%20of%20gardening%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189744%2Fbangalore-lifestyle-one-day-holiday-village-rural-pottery-green-trip-village-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rural%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20building%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20has%20stretched%20their%20understanding%20in%20these%20regards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20invite%20us%20into%20their%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358212%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Raghav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20built%20with%20cob%20which%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20sand%2C%20clay%2C%20straw%2C%20soil%20and%20water%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-2_11zon-1721812497-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358214%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20built%20with%20cob%2C%20which%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20sand%2C%20clay%2C%20straw%2C%20soil%20and%20water%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Raghav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKnock%20on%20sustainability%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20passed%20by%20Dhunar%20Gaon%20in%20Rishikesh%20in%202021%2C%20was%20met%20with%20an%20unusual%20sight.%20Albanian%20folk%20songs%20reverberated%20through%20the%20air%2C%20interrupted%20only%20by%20the%20beats%20of%20Japanese%20rock%20music%2C%20German%20techno%2C%20and%20Daler%20Mehndi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ETunak%20Tunak%20Tun%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20grooving%20to%20these%20lively%20tempos%20were%20a%20group%20of%2090%20individuals.%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20them%20would%20reveal%20their%20vivid%20origins%20%E2%80%94%20Brazil%2C%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20Canada%2C%20Slovenia%20%E2%80%94%2018%20nationalities%2C%20to%20be%20precise%2C%20Ansh%20states.%20Their%20rhythms%20though%20unchoreographed%2C%20would%20seem%20almost%20synced%20to%20an%20onlooker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20distracted%20by%20their%20moves%2C%20Ansh%20urges%2C%20look%20under%20their%20feet%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FOtYaplok1Z8%3Fsi%3DtIHOIpE9o8aOTj38%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20material%20the%20group%20spent%20months%20dancing%20upon%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCob%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20clay%2C%20sand%2C%20soil%2C%20straw%20and%20water.%20We%20chopped%20wheat%20and%20rice%20straw%2C%20put%20it%20on%20a%20tarp%2C%20and%20then%20invited%20the%20group%20to%20dance%20on%20it%20until%20it%20formed%20a%20burrito-shaped%20dough.%20Once%20stable%2C%20the%20dough%20does%20not%20break%20and%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20building%20material.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20they%20brought%20in%20foreign%20hands%20for%20the%20project%2C%20Raghav%20laughs%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20planned.%20We%20put%20out%20a%20request%20on%20the%20website%20%E2%80%98Workaway%E2%80%99%2C%20asking%20people%20interested%20in%20sustainable%20building%20to%20join%20us.%20Through%20the%20months%2C%20we%20got%20many%20who%20were%20keen%20on%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20these%20were%20people%20who%20did%20not%20specially%20make%20a%20trip%20to%20dance%20on%20the%20cob.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20already%20heading%20to%20Rishikesh%20for%20a%20vacation.%20But%20their%20interest%20in%20natural%20building%20attracted%20them%20to%20our%20site.%20We%20set%20up%20a%20dorm%20for%20them%20in%20the%20village%20Umrisen%2C%20where%20we%20were%20camping%20out%20during%20the%20construction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAishwarya%20Lakhani%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20this%20community%20effort%2C%20says%20she%20had%20always%20been%20meaning%20to%20get%20into%20conscious%20design.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20across%20this%20project%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity.%20I%20had%20been%20wanting%20to%20go%20to%20Tiny%20Farm%20Lab%20for%20months%20and%20since%20it%20was%20coinciding%20with%20my%20Rishikesh%20travel%20dates%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20head%20there.%20Right%20from%20day%20one%2C%20it%20was%20a%20warm%20experience%20staying%20with%20the%20villagers.%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20took%20good%20care%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20echoes%20the%20thoughts%20of%20the%20others%20when%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20in%20awe%20that%20such%20a%20thing%20could%20be%20achieved%20in%20a%20remote%20location.%20Having%20practised%20with%20reusable%20materials%20and%20natural%20plasters%20myself%2C%20it%20%5Bthis%20project%5D%20gave%20me%20hope%20and%20inspiration%20knowing%20that%20the%20sky%20is%20the%20limit%20when%20using%20cob%20for%20built%20environments.%20Working%20with%20cob%20grounds%20you.%20Dancing%20on%20the%20mud%20is%20an%20emotion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20Rolaniya%2C%20an%20architect%2C%20seconds%20Lakhani.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20mud%2C%20specifically%20cob%20was%20very%20intuitive%20to%20me.%20Being%20a%20natural%20building%20construction%20practitioner%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20working%20with%20cob.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20like%20finding%20yourself.%20In%20architecture%2C%20one%20tends%20to%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20transforming%20a%20building%2C%20but%20working%20with%20mud%20and%20cob%20shows%20you%20that%20it%20goes%20both%20ways%20%E2%80%94%20they%20transform%20you%20in%20turn%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20the%20brother%20duo%20three%20years%20to%20build%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort.%20They%20recall%20the%20journey%20as%20revelationary%20in%20many%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20two%20city%20kids%20who%20did%20not%20know%20much%2C%20we%20learnt%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ansh.%20%E2%80%9CTravelling%20from%20the%20last%20motorable%20point%20in%20Phoolchatti%20to%20the%20Umrisen%20village%20involved%20crossing%20a%20wooden%20bridge%20across%20a%20tributary%20Heval%20and%20then%20hiking%20for%201.5%20km.%20Each%20time%20we%20had%20to%20get%20groceries%2C%20we%20had%20to%20make%20a%2020%20km%20trek.%E2%80%9D%20But%20the%20effort%20was%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-3-1721812808.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20comprises%20a%20loft%20bed%2C%20a%20cave%20bedroom%2C%20a%20kitchenette%2C%20and%20a%20bathroom%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-3-1721812808.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-3-1721812808-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-3-1721812808-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com