2C%20underscoring%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20skilled%20labour.%20To%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%20vocational%20training%20in%20construction%20has%20become%20essential%2C%20equipping%20the%20workforce%20with%20specialised%20skills%20vital%20for%20the%20sector%E2%80%99s%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20this%20need%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20launched%20the%20first%20Construction%20Skills%20Training%20Institute%20(CSTI)%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20in%201995.%20This%20initiative%20aimed%20to%20develop%20a%20cadre%20of%20well-trained%20professionals%20for%20the%20construction%20industry.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20CSTI%20has%20expanded%20to%20nine%20operational%20institutes%2C%20training%20over%203.4%20lakh%20workers%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkilled%20youth%20trained%20at%20these%20CSTIs%20are%20now%20employed%20by%20top%20construction%20companies%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20L%26amp%3BT%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20skilled%20workers%20to%20boost%20livelihoods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20goals%20behind%20this%20endeavour%20by%20the%20company%20is%20to%20help%20underprivileged%20rural%20youth%20become%20self-reliant%20through%20this%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L%26amp%3BT%20runs%20nine%20CSTIs%20in%20the%20country%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c